data.description: Check out this ONE STORY 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in Jenks School District nestled in Shady Oaks Estates! The home has a spacious foyer,  2 living rooms, and a huge office / optional 4th bedroom with wood built-ins. The first living room features a vaulted ceiling with a wood beam, and large windows overlooking a terraced backyard with mature trees. The second living room is a hardwood paneled den with a fireplace, walk-in wet bar, and access to the back patio. The dining behind the kitchen has natural light. Vaulted ceilings in the master with French doors and windows to let in a nice breeze! The master bathroom has a soaking tub and separate shower. Very neat backyard with a patio walled in by stone, offering tons of privacy! Stone stairs from the patio lead up to the wooded portion of the yard with nice, mature trees. This home could be converted to a Midcentury Modern Dream Home with the right touch ~ lots of windows with natural light, and various points to access the one-of-a-kind landscape surrounding the home. Rare find in a fantastic part of Tulsa ~ Come see this home today!
